title: Run db:seed to populate FO-08 prompts
description:
Run the database seed command to populate FO-08 prompts in the KV store.

Command to run:
```bash
npm run db:seed
```

This seeds all FO-08 prompts into the KV store so the agents can use them.

⚠️ Do not close this tick until the seed completes successfully.
acceptance_criteria: npm run db:seed completes without errors
